# nexus /.turn — per-turn / per-kick policy SSOT
# Implements hive raw 89 turn-SSOT-forward-spec (FORWARD SPEC, status=new).
# nexus interpretation: "turn" = single ω-cycle (kick) execution. Coding-agent
# 컨텍스트의 LLM-turn 이 아니라, nexus 의 atomic 작업 단위인 kick 1회.
# Created 2026-04-27.
#
# Compliance ramp:
#   week 1-2  schema lock + tool/kick_dispatch.hexa --enforce-turn-policy 플래그 wiring
#   week 3-4  parallel-kick concurrency cap (today's incident: 3 unbounded parallel kicks)
#   week 5-6  cost-log per-kick row schema (state/audit/kick_costs.jsonl, raw 77)
#   week 7-12 raw 1 os-lock 확장 (chflags uchg .turn) + warn → live 전환
#
# Until raw 1 os-lock 가 .turn 으로 확장될 때까지 advisory.

turn-policy 1 new "default per-kick policy (ω-cycle scope)"
  slug turn-policy-kick-default
  budget-cap-cost-units 50000
  rate-limit-turns-per-minute 3
  timeout-seconds-per-turn 1800
  root-cause-first-enforcement true
  cost-attribution-cost-center nexus-kick-default
  enforce-layer hive-agent
  enforce-layer-rationale per hive raw 89 — hive-agent contract layer; tool/kick_dispatch.hexa consumes policy at kick start; OS-level cannot evaluate per-kick semantic policy.
  why ω-cycle (kick) 이 nexus 의 primary 작업 단위. 2026-04-27 incident — 3개 kick 을 axes/falsifier/parent-sid 미설정으로 병렬 발사하여 budget overrun + workflow violation 발생. .turn 이 그 실패 모드를 캡쳐.
  scope nexus tool/kick_dispatch.hexa + cli/run.hexa kick subcommand + cross-host backend dispatch (ubu1/ubu2/htz)
  proof tool/kick_dispatch.hexa
  proof state/audit/kick_costs.jsonl (forward — raw 77 schema, week 5-6)
  follow-up tool/kick_dispatch.hexa --enforce-turn-policy 플래그 (read .turn at start, abort on cap breach)
  follow-up parallel-kick concurrency cap declaration — 현재 uncapped, 동시 N 제한 도입
  follow-up cost-log integration — emit cost_actual per kick to state/audit/kick_costs.jsonl

turn-policy 2 new "drill-batch policy (long-running, larger budget)"
  slug turn-policy-drill-batch
  budget-cap-cost-units 200000
  rate-limit-turns-per-minute 1
  timeout-seconds-per-turn 7200
  root-cause-first-enforcement true
  cost-attribution-cost-center nexus-drill-batch
  enforce-layer hive-agent
  enforce-layer-rationale drill-batch 는 다중 angle DFS — kick 보다 4× budget + 4× timeout 허용. raw 86 cost-attribution 으로 격리.
  why drill batch (5-lens DFS, T3→T4 85→95% breakthrough criteria) 는 단일 kick 보다 본질적으로 무거움. 별도 cost-center 로 cap 분리.
  scope tool/drill_batch.hexa + tool/drill_breakthrough_runner.hexa
  proof tool/drill_batch.hexa
  proof shared/bench/drill_breakthrough_criteria.json
  follow-up drill_batch concurrency cap (1, exclusive — 동시 다중 drill 금지)

# Cross-reference:
# hive /.turn turn-policy-default 는 hive packages/coding-agent 인터랙티브 세션용.
# nexus /.turn 는 ω-cycle (kick) + drill 단위. 두 surface 는 cost-center 가 다르므로
# raw 86 cost-attribution 에서 격리되어 budget collision 없음.

# follow-up (raw 89 compliance ramp, nexus-specific):
#   1. raw#2 self-format keys whitelist — hive 와 동일 키 재사용 (확장 불필요)
#   2. tool/kick_dispatch.hexa — turn-policy 강제 게이트 추가
#   3. parallel-kick lock — 동시 N 제한 (default 2)
#   4. cost-log integration — emit cost_actual per kick to state/audit/kick_costs.jsonl
#   5. raw 1 os-lock 확장 — chflags uchg .turn (week 7-12)
